Omege UOS Memory Test Tool
==========================

This is Omege UOS operating system of memory test tool source code GitHub repository.

Quick Start
-------------
Website: https://www.omegeuos.top/en-us/
License: https://github.com/deeplearning-corporation/memtest/blob/main/LICENSE/
Docs: https://docs.omegeuos.top/

1.Welcome
--------
Welcome to Omege UOS memory test tool of source tree GitHub repository.

2.Compile
---------
If you needs compile the Omege UOS memory test you needs of applications:
GCC
Make

3.Run
-----
If you needs run the Omege UOS memory test you can download the ISO image file can press F8 key to Boot Menu. choose the Memory Test Tool.
after Memory Test tool is running your PC.

4.Legal
-------

The Omege UOS memory test tool is using MIT License is open-source.
